<p><b>Special Rapporteur on the promotion and protection of human rights while countering 
terrorism 
</b></p>
<p>106. At the 14th meeting, on 10 March 2009, the Special Rapporteur on the promotion and 
protection of human rights while countering terrorism, Martin Scheinin, presented his report 
(A/HRC/10/3 and Add.1 and 2). 
</p>
<p>107. At the same meeting, the representative of Spain made a statement as a concerned country. 
</p>
