Netherlands, Republic of Korea, Slovakia, Slovenia, Ukraine, United 
Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland; 
</p>
<p><i>Abstaining</i>: Chile, Mexico, Switzerland. 
</p>
<p>172. For the text as adopted, see A/HRC/10/L.11, resolution 10/11. 
</p>
