<p><i>Abstaining</i>: Angola, Azerbaijan, Bangladesh, Bolivia, Brazil, Djibouti, Gabon, India, 
Malaysia, Nicaragua, Pakistan, Philippines, Qatar, Senegal, South Africa. 
</p>
