<p><b>46</b> Observer of the Council speaking on behalf of States members and observer States. </p>

 <p> 
</p><p>696. At the same meeting, at the request of the representative of Germany (on behalf of States 
members of the European Union that are members of the Council), a recorded vote was taken 
